类 ElfDynamicStructure

java.lang.Object
net.fornwall.jelf.ElfDynamicStructure
public class ElfDynamicStructure extends Object
http://www.sco.com/developers/gabi/latest/ch5.dynamic.html#dynamic_section "If an object file participates in dynamic linking, its program header table will have an element of type PT_DYNAMIC. This ``segment'' contains the .dynamic section. A special symbol, _DYNAMIC, labels the section, which contains an array of the following structures." 
 typedef struct { Elf32_Sword d_tag; union { Elf32_Word d_val; Elf32_Addr d_ptr; } d_un; } Elf32_Dyn;
 extern Elf32_Dyn _DYNAMIC[];
 
 typedef struct { Elf64_Sxword d_tag; union { Elf64_Xword d_val; Elf64_Addr d_ptr; } d_un; } Elf64_Dyn;
 extern Elf64_Dyn _DYNAMIC[];
